Update internal build structure for TensorBoard Polymer dependencies

TensorBoard is currently migrating to Polymer 3:
<https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorboard/issues/3887>
This includes a change to the Google-internal build structure, which
TFMA depends on. The build structure is not exposed in open source.
